Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, the premier bowling alley experience. My name is Alex. How can I assist you today?

Hi Alex, I have some questions about my billing statement.

Certainly! To better assist you, could I have your name, please?

Sure, my name is Jamie.

Thank you, Jamie. Can you please provide your customer ID number so I can access your billing information?

Yes, of course. It's one, two, three, four, five.

Great, thank you. Could you also verify the last four digits of the phone number associated with your account?

Sure, it's five, six, seven, eight.

Perfect. I see your account now. What questions do you have about your billing statement?

I noticed a higher charge this month, and I'm not sure why.

I understand your concern. Let me look into this for you. Please hold on for a moment.

No problem.

Thank you for your patience, Jamie. It seems there was an additional charge for lanes reserved on the weekend special. Does that sound correct?

Ah, yes, now I remember. Thanks for clarifying that.

You're welcome! Is there anything else I can help you with today?

No, that's all. Thanks for your help, Alex.

You're very welcome, Jamie. Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a great day!
